      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This specific unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and professional subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension remains tight with factory-spec bushings and dampers, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are known for. Presented in concours condition with flawless paint and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key example for the technical purist.",
